\c 56
\s Dhavhidhi anochema nokuda kwavavengi vake
\d Kumutungamiri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weNjiva iri mumioki iri kure. Pisarema raDhavhidhi; rwiyo rweMikitami; panguva yaakabatwa navaFirisitia paâ€‘
\s Gati.
\p
\v 56
\v 1 Ndinzwirei tsitsi, Mwari; nokuti vanhu vanotsvaka kundimedza;
\s Zuva rose vanorwa neni
\s vachindimanikidza.
\p
\v 2 Vavengi vangu vanoda kundimedza zuva rose;
\s Nokuti vanorwa neni
\s vachizvikudza vazhinji.
\p
\v 3 Panguva yandinotya,
\s Ndichavimba nemi.
\p
\v 4 MunaMwari ndicharumbidza shoko rake;
\s Ndakavimba naMwari, handingatyi; Nyama ingandiiteiko?
\p
\v 5 Zuva rose vanoshandura mashoko angu;
\s Mifungo yavo yose inondifungira zvakaipa.
\p
\v 6 Vanoungana, vanovanda, Vanocherekedza makwara angu, Kana vachivandira mweya wangu.
\p
\v 7 Vachapukunyuka nenzira
\s yezvakaipa here?
\s Paradzai vanhu nokutsamwa kwenyu, Mwari.
\p
\v 8 Imi munoverenga madzungairiro angu;
\s Isai misodzi yangu mumudziyo yenyu; Haizi murugwaro rwenyu here?
\p
\v 9 ipapo vavengi vangu vachadzokera shure nomusi wandinodana; Ndinoziva chinhu ichi, kuti
\s Mwari ari kurutivi rwangu.
\p
\v 10 MunaMwari ndicharumbidza shoko rake;
\s MunaJehovha ndicharumbidza shoko rake.
\p
\v 11 Ndakavimba naMwari, handingatyi; Vanhu vangandiiteiko?
\p
\v 12 Ndinosungwa nezvandakakupikirai Mwari;
\s Ndichakuvigirai zvipiriso
\s zvokuvonga nazvo.
\p
\v 13 Nokuti makarwira mweya wangu parufu;
\s Namakumbo angu pakugumburwa. Kuti ndifambe pamberi paMwari Muchiedza choupenyu.
